WEBVTT

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.500
[On-screen text] From the creators of Tangled and Wreck-It Ralph.

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:06.000
[On-screen text] Disney.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:09.200
[Audio description] A carrot-nosed, coal-eyed snowman shuffles

00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:12.800
[Audio description] up to a purple flower peeping out of deep snow.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:14.000
Hello.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:18.800
[Audio description] He takes a deep sniff. AAAAchoo!

00:00:18.800 --> 00:00:22.200
[Audio description] His nose lands on a frozen pond.

00:00:22.200 --> 00:00:24.800
[Audio description] A reindeer looks up and pants like a dog.

00:00:24.800 --> 00:00:26.800
[Audio description] Seeing the reindeer slip on the ice,

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:28.800
[Audio description] the snowman smiles and moves toward him,

00:00:28.800 --> 00:00:31.000
[Audio description] though actually he's running on the spot.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:33.000
[Audio description] The reindeer falls on his chin.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:35.500
[Audio description] The snowman uses his arm as a crutch.

00:00:35.500 --> 00:00:38.000
[Audio description] The reindeer paddles his front legs.

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:40.500
[Audio description] Head over heels, the snowman crawls along the ice.

00:00:40.500 --> 00:00:42.800
[Audio description] The reindeer does the breaststroke.

00:00:42.800 --> 00:00:46.000
[Audio description] The snowman rolls his body, but flips onto his back.

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:49.000
[Audio description] The reindeer's tongue sticks to the ice.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:52.000
[Audio description] Ahh. The snowman, hurls his head, twig arm,

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:56.000
[Audio description] and reindeer lips tug at the carrot.

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:57.500
[Audio description] The carrot flies off and lands in soft snow.

00:00:57.500 --> 00:01:01.000
[Audio description] Ahh. The reindeer goes after it with the snowman

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:04.000
[Audio description] and his body parts hanging on his tail.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:07.000
[Audio description] The snowman puts himself back together again.

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:10.500
[Audio description] He glumly contemplates his noseless state.

00:01:10.500 --> 00:01:13.000
[Audio description] The reindeer jams the carrot back in place

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:15.500
[Audio description] and pants like a proud puppy.

00:01:15.500 --> 00:01:18.500
[Audio description] The snowman pats him with a stick thin arm.

00:01:18.500 --> 00:01:21.000
[Audio description] Then he goes to sneeze.

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.500
[Audio description] He grabs his nose with both hands.

00:01:23.500 --> 00:01:26.000
[Audio description] His head shoots off.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:27.500
[On-screen text] Frozen.

00:01:27.500 --> 00:01:30.500
[On-screen text] Coming this winter in 3D.
